\c 36
\s Vana vaEsau
\p
\v 1 Ndiyowo nhoroondo yedzinza raEsau unova Edhomu:
\v 2 Esau wakatora vakadzi vake kuvakunda veKenani: Adha mukunda waEroni muHeti, naAhoribhama mukunda waAna mukunda waZibhioni muHivhi,
\v 3 naBhasimati mukunda waIshimaeri hanzvadzi yaNebhayoti.
\v 4 Adha ndokuberekera Esau Erifazi; Bhasimati ndokubereka Rueri;
\v 5 Ahoribhama ndokubereka Jeushi naJarami naKora; ava vanakomana vaEsau, vaakaberekerwa panyika yeKenani.
\v 6 Zvino Esau wakatora vakadzi vake nevanakomana vake nevakunda vake, nemweya yese yeimba yake, nemombe dzake nezvipfuwo zvake zvese, nenhumbi dzake dzese dzaakange awana munyika yeKenani, ndokuenda kune \add imwe \add*nyika achibva pachiso chaJakove munin'ina wake.
\v 7 Nokuti zvipfuwo zvavo zvakange zvakawandisa kuti vagare pamwe, uye nyika yeutorwa hwavo yakange isingagoni kuvatakura nekuda kwezvipfuwo zvavo.
\v 8 Esau ndokugara kugomo reSeiri; Esau ndiye Edhomu.
\p
\v 9 Zvino awa marudzi aEsau, baba veVaEdhomu, kugomo reSeiri;
\v 10 awa mazita evanakomana vaEsau: Erifazi mwanakomana waAdha mukadzi waEsau, Rueri mwanakomana waBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\v 11 Nevanakomana vaErifazi vaiva Temani, Omari, Zefo, naGatamu, naKenazi.
\v 12 Zvino Timuna waiva murongo waErifazi mwanakomana waEsau; wakaberekera Erifazi Amareki; ava vanakomana vaAdha mukadzi waEsau.
\v 13 Zvino ava vaiva vanakomana vaRueri: Nahati naZera, Shama naMiza; ava vanakomana vaBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\p
\v 14 Zvino ava vaiva vanakomana vaOhoribhama mukunda waAna mukunda waZibhioni mukadzi waEsau; ndokuberekera Esau Jeushi naJarami naKora.
\p
\v 15 Awa madzishe evana vaEsau: Vanakomana vaErifazi dangwe raEsau: Ishe Temani, ishe Omari, ishe Zefo, ishe Kenazi,
\v 16 ishe Kora, ishe Gatamu, ishe Amareki; awa madzishe aErifazi munyika yeEdhomu; ava vanakomana vaAdha.
\p
\v 17 Uye ava vanakomana vaRueri mwanakomana waEsau: Ishe Nahati, ishe Zera, ishe Shama, ishe Miza; awa madzishe aRueri munyika yeEdhomu; ava vanakomana vaBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\p
\v 18 Uye ava vanakomana vaAhoribhama mukadzi waEsau: Ishe Jeushi, ishe Jarami, ishe Kora; ava madzishe aAhoribhama mukunda waAna mukadzi waEsau.
\v 19 Ava vanakomana vaEsau, uye awa madzishe avo; unova Edhomu.
\p
\v 20 Ava vanakomana vaSeiri muHori, vagari venyika: Rotani naShobhari naZibhioni naAna
\v 21 naDhishoni naEzeri naDhishani; ava madzishe eVaHori, vanakomana vaSeiri munyika yeEdhomu.
\v 22 Uye vanakomana vaRotani vaiva Hori naHemami; nehanzvadzi yaRotani aiva Timuna.
\v 23 Uye ava vanakomana vaShobharu: Arivhani, naManahati, naEbhari, Shefo, naOnamu.
\v 24 Uye ava vanakomana vaZibhioni: Vese Aja naAna; ndiAna akawana matsime \add emvura\add* inopisa murenje achifudza mbongoro dzaZibhioni baba vake.
\v 25 Uye ava vanakomana vaAna: Dhishoni naAhoribhama, mukunda waAna.
\p
\v 26 Uye ava vanakomana vaDhishani: Hemudhani naEshibhani naIturani naKerani.
\v 27 Ava vanakomana vaEzeri: Bhirihani naZaavhani naAkani.
\v 28 Ava vanakomana vaDhishani: Uzi naArani.
\v 29 Ava madzishe eVaHori: Ishe Rotani, ishe Shobharu, ishe Zibhioni, ishe Ana,
\v 30 ishe Dhishoni, ishe Ezeri, ishe Dhishani; awa madzishe eVaHori, nemadzishe avo munyika yeSeiri.
\p
\v 31 Uye awa madzimambo akatonga munyika yeEdhomu, pasati pambotonga mambo pavana vaIsraeri.
\v 32 Uye Bhera mwanakomana waBheori wakatonga paEdhomu, uye zita reguta rake raiva Dhinihabha.
\v 33 Zvino Bhera wakafa, Jobhabhu mwanakomana waZera weBhozara ndokutonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 34 Jobhabhu ndokufa, Hushamu wenyika yavaTemani ndokutonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 35 Hushamu ndokufa; Hadhadhi mwanakomana waBhedhadhi, iye akarova Midhiani kusango reMoabhu, akatonga pachinzvimbo chake; uye zita reguta rake raiva Avhiti.
\v 36 Hadhadhi ndokufa; Samura weMasereka ndokutonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 37 Samura ndokufa; Shauri weRehobhoti parwizi akatonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 38 Shauri ndokufa; Bhaari-Hanani mwanakomana waAkibhori ndokutonga pachinzvimbo chake.
\v 39 Bhaari-Hanani mwanakomana waAkibhori ndokufa, Hadhari ndokutonga pachinzvimbo chake; uye zita reguta rake raiva Pau; nezita romukadzi wake raiva Mehetabheri, mukunda waMatiredhi, mukunda waMezahabhi.
\p
\v 40 Uye awa mazita emadzishe ekwaEsau, zvichienderana nemhuri dzavo, zvichienderana nenzvimbo dzawo, nemazita avo: Ishe Timuna, ishe Arivha, ishe Jeteti,
\v 41 ishe Ohoribhama, ishe Era, ishe Pinoni,
\v 42 ishe Kenazi, ishe Temani, ishe Mibhizari,
\v 43 ishe Magidhieri, ishe Iramu; awa madzishe aEdhomu, maererano nenzvimbo dzavo dzekugara, munyika yenhaka yavo. Uyu ndiEsau, baba vaEdhomu.